7
00:01:56,239 --> 00:01:57,299
Do you like Miao Jing?

8
00:02:01,879 --> 00:02:03,379
I just don't want to embarrass her.

9
00:02:03,760 --> 00:02:05,040
Don't pretend.

10
00:02:06,299 --> 00:02:08,080
You obviously just can't let go.

11
00:02:10,180 --> 00:02:10,879
Chen Yi,

12
00:02:11,599 --> 00:02:13,719
Miao Jing turned down top universities outside the city,

13
00:02:13,780 --> 00:02:14,800
