15
00:02:15,879 --> 00:02:16,960
Don't you understand?

16
00:02:18,080 --> 00:02:19,360
Can you take responsibility for her choice?

17
00:02:20,599 --> 00:02:21,599
You only care about the moment.

18
00:02:21,960 --> 00:02:23,199
Have you ever thought about her future?

19
00:02:23,580 --> 00:02:24,080
Have you ever thought about

20
00:02:24,080 --> 00:02:24,919
your future?

21
00:02:25,300 --> 00:02:25,740
Have you ever thought about

22
00:02:25,740 --> 00:02:26,780
your own future?

23
00:02:43,840 --> 00:02:44,539
What's wrong?

24
00:02:46,800 --> 00:02:47,639
Something wrong with the car.

25
00:03:02,120 --> 00:03:02,840
The car broke down.

26
00:03:06,800 --> 00:03:08,099
Let's find somewhere to shelter from the rain first.

27
00:03:58,740 --> 00:03:59,360
Are you cold?

28
00:04:27,800 --> 00:04:29,079
Wen is right.

29
00:04:30,399 --> 00:04:31,579
I want to stay here

30
00:04:32,240 --> 00:04:33,399
not because I'm attached to my home.

31
00:04:48,980 --> 00:04:50,279
Don't make fun of your future

32
00:04:52,699 --> 00:04:53,600
Vineton City is too small.

33
00:04:55,339 --> 00:04:56,199
Like our home.

34
00:04:56,839 --> 00:04:57,560
You can't live there

35
00:04:57,560 --> 00:04:58,100
all your life.

36
00:05:03,959 --> 00:05:05,040
Sooner or later you'll have to move

37
00:05:05,040 --> 00:05:06,199
to a bigger and better house.

38
00:05:09,600 --> 00:05:10,779
A house is not a home.

39
00:05:13,360 --> 00:05:14,240
You know

40
00:05:15,579 --> 00:05:17,060
what I cherish the most.

41
00:06:38,259 --> 00:06:39,600
Will you wait for me to come back?

42
00:06:47,259 --> 00:06:47,939
Miao Jing,

43
00:06:52,399 --> 00:06:53,699
you are the only family I have.

44
00:06:57,699 --> 00:06:58,939
Whenever you come back,

45
00:07:02,339 --> 00:07:03,500
I'll be there for you.

46
00:08:05,300 --> 00:08:05,740
It has been fixed.

47
00:08:07,620 --> 00:08:08,439
Okay.

48
00:08:19,100 --> 00:08:19,720
Chen Yi,

49
00:08:20,360 --> 00:08:22,120
let's go eat hot pot after checking the score.

50
00:08:27,699 --> 00:08:28,199
Okay.

51
00:09:16,500 --> 00:09:17,200
Pick one.

52
00:09:25,340 --> 00:09:25,759
You...

53
00:09:26,100 --> 00:09:27,860
You go down in the middle of the night to buy popsicles.

54
00:09:29,379 --> 00:09:29,940
Hurry.

55
00:09:30,059 --> 00:09:31,519
It will almost melt if you drag your feet.

56
00:09:31,700 --> 00:09:32,360
I've taken one.

57
00:09:33,299 --> 00:09:34,019
Open the door.

58
00:10:58,120 --> 00:11:00,360
Six hundred and twenty.

59
00:11:02,379 --> 00:11:03,100
I should be able to

60
00:11:03,100 --> 00:11:04,919
