61
00:11:11,379 --> 00:11:12,559
Tomorrow at 11:30 noon,

62
00:11:12,679 --> 00:11:13,480
Vineton Hotel.

63
00:11:13,700 --> 00:11:14,480
Don't forget, everyone.

64
00:11:14,879 --> 00:11:16,100
Got it.

65
00:11:16,519 --> 00:11:17,220
What about Miao Jing?

66
00:11:17,600 --> 00:11:18,460
Is she in our group chat?

67
00:11:18,700 --> 00:11:19,620
Remind her about tomorrow.

68
00:11:19,940 --> 00:11:20,740
Why remain silent?

69
00:11:21,039 --> 00:11:22,139
At least half of the people in the group

70
00:11:22,139 --> 00:11:23,059
had a crush on Miao Jing.

71
00:11:23,299 --> 00:11:24,360
They're too scared to confess.

72
00:11:26,000 --> 00:11:27,679
There must be many who fell for Miao Jing.

73
00:11:27,860 --> 00:11:29,179
She might have been secretly in love.

74
00:11:30,919 --> 00:11:31,759
In love?

75
00:11:32,740 --> 00:11:34,159
I'd love to fall in love.

76
00:12:41,379 --> 00:12:42,340
Whether the salary can be paid as usual,

77
00:12:42,340 --> 00:12:43,059
I don't know.

78
00:12:44,460 --> 00:12:45,440
Let's wait for Mr. Hu to ask.

79
00:12:47,580 --> 00:12:48,080
Here comes.

80
00:12:50,480 --> 00:12:51,159
Mr. Chen.

81
00:12:53,100 --> 00:12:54,539
What a damn hot day!

82
00:12:55,019 --> 00:12:55,500
Mr. Hu,

83
00:12:55,899 --> 00:12:56,820
any news on the construction period?

84
00:12:57,080 --> 00:12:57,679
Xu,

85
00:12:58,340 --> 00:12:59,799
I was about to tell you.

86
00:13:00,500 --> 00:13:01,940
This project we're working on

87
00:13:01,940 --> 00:13:02,700
