95
00:13:17,039 --> 00:13:18,580
Wages will be settled on the actual working dates.

96
00:13:19,059 --> 00:13:19,899
The finance team

97
00:13:20,019 --> 00:13:20,960
will walk you through the exact process.

98
00:13:22,500 --> 00:13:23,539
Just ask me if you have any questions.

99
00:13:27,860 --> 00:13:28,220
But...

100
00:13:28,940 --> 00:13:29,700
This project was going smoothly.

101
00:13:29,779 --> 00:13:30,899
