102
00:13:31,039 --> 00:13:31,379
Then...

103
00:13:33,860 --> 00:13:34,460
Mr. Chen,

104
00:13:35,679 --> 00:13:36,320
that's not fair.

105
00:13:37,879 --> 00:13:38,799
College students,

106
00:13:39,279 --> 00:13:39,940
not only this project

107
00:13:39,940 --> 00:13:41,500
