110
00:13:45,019 --> 00:13:46,340
If you've got any complaints,

111
00:13:46,399 --> 00:13:47,639
take it up with Mr. Zhai.

112
00:13:48,299 --> 00:13:49,700
You are a matter of one sentence,

113
00:13:49,940 --> 00:13:50,860
