134
00:16:00,360 --> 00:16:01,259
Do you know Green Lai?

135
00:16:02,539 --> 00:16:03,019
Green Lai?

136
00:16:04,200 --> 00:16:04,860
A few years ago,

137
00:16:04,860 --> 00:16:06,220
