138
00:16:06,659 --> 00:16:07,500
Yeah.

139
00:16:07,779 --> 00:16:10,379
It is also Mr. Zhai's business.

140
00:16:10,820 --> 00:16:11,740
Even though the matter was so chaotic

141
00:16:11,740 --> 00:16:12,759
