145
00:16:21,559 --> 00:16:23,379
Mr. Zhai can handle it.

146
00:16:24,320 --> 00:16:25,740
It's the same this time.

147
00:16:26,159 --> 00:16:27,960
They won't last a few days.

148
00:16:33,879 --> 00:16:34,519
You see.

149
00:16:37,679 --> 00:16:38,460
What kind of tea is this?

150
00:16:38,740 --> 00:16:39,559
It smells good.

151
00:16:39,980 --> 00:16:41,440
This is a great thing.

152
00:16:41,940 --> 00:16:44,100
This is the best Pu'er tea.

153
00:16:45,740 --> 00:16:47,980
A few days ago,

154
00:16:47,980 --> 00:16:49,360
Zhai Fengmao ordered a batch of vintage Pu'er tea

155
00:16:49,360 --> 00:16:51,500
through me at the auction house in Gangcheng.

156
00:16:55,059 --> 00:16:55,860
Who are these teas for?

157
00:16:59,159 --> 00:17:00,740
If those inspection team guys

158
00:17:00,740 --> 00:17:01,480
weren't such idiots,

159
00:17:02,259 --> 00:17:03,759
