160
00:17:04,220 --> 00:17:05,420
I've already told them

161
00:17:05,420 --> 00:17:06,599
that I am from Zhai's side,

162
00:17:06,599 --> 00:17:07,880
but they don't let me in.

163
00:17:10,319 --> 00:17:10,759
If they hadn't

164
00:17:10,759 --> 00:17:12,240
dug up those tax invoices,

165
00:17:12,380 --> 00:17:14,319
even if the God were to come,

166
00:17:14,480 --> 00:17:14,839
I would still

167
00:17:14,839 --> 00:17:16,440
teach him a lesson.

168
00:17:23,619 --> 00:17:23,980
Hello.

169
00:17:24,119 --> 00:17:24,759
Take a look at the documents.

170
00:17:32,480 --> 00:17:32,920
Arrived.

171
00:17:36,900 --> 00:17:37,700
The security here

172
00:17:37,940 --> 00:17:39,140
is so strict.

173
00:17:40,500 --> 00:17:41,180
How did your company transfer you

174
00:17:41,180 --> 00:17:42,640
here to work the night shift.

175
00:17:43,700 --> 00:17:44,940
Their inspection team for pyramid schemes

176
00:17:44,940 --> 00:17:46,000
is meeting here.

177
00:17:46,099 --> 00:17:47,099
And those documents

178
00:17:47,099 --> 00:17:48,359
need guarding overnight.

179
00:17:50,539 --> 00:17:51,180
The wedding dress that

180
00:17:51,180 --> 00:17:52,539
I really wanted to try is this one.

181
00:17:53,799 --> 00:17:54,859
Unfortunately, in the bridal shop,

182
00:17:54,859 --> 00:17:56,099
I didn't try it.

183
00:17:59,660 --> 00:18:01,019
Esteemed Mr. Zhou,

184
00:18:01,220 --> 00:18:02,900
when exactly are you free?

185
00:18:03,299 --> 00:18:04,220
I've changed times with

186
00:18:04,220 --> 00:18:05,519
the photographer twice.

187
00:18:06,960 --> 00:18:07,539
Okay.

188
00:18:07,640 --> 00:18:08,400
Honey.

189
00:18:09,079 --> 00:18:10,200
After this busy time,

190
00:18:10,859 --> 00:18:12,480
I'll take a better shot with you.

191
00:18:13,039 --> 00:18:13,599
Is that okay?

192
00:18:14,579 --> 00:18:15,240
You promise.

193
00:18:15,819 --> 00:18:16,619
I promise.

194
00:18:17,039 --> 00:18:17,500
I promise.

195
00:18:17,500 --> 00:18:18,400
I promise you.

196
00:18:23,859 --> 00:18:25,099
Isn't that Mr. Zhao of the tax bureau?

197
00:18:26,119 --> 00:18:27,559
Why's he involved in pyramid scheme investigations?

198
00:18:28,900 --> 00:18:29,619
Pyramid schemes?

199
00:18:31,380 --> 00:18:32,839
The Green Lai incident

200
00:18:33,180 --> 00:18:33,859
was supposed to be closed

201
00:18:33,859 --> 00:18:35,059
a few years ago, wasn't it?

202
00:18:37,460 --> 00:18:39,000
Didn't you just say pyramid schemes?

203
00:18:39,500 --> 00:18:40,779
Inspection team to investigate pyramid schemes.

204
00:18:43,180 --> 00:18:44,759
Those people ask to investigate Green Lai every day,

205
00:18:44,759 --> 00:18:45,640
so I get confused.

206
00:18:45,859 --> 00:18:46,660
It's not a pyramid scheme.

207
00:18:46,660 --> 00:18:47,299
It's a tax fraud.

208
00:18:51,099 --> 00:18:52,640
Was security this tight before?

209
00:18:53,420 --> 00:18:54,960
No.

210
00:18:55,099 --> 00:18:56,380
They only beefed up patrols

211
00:18:56,380 --> 00:18:57,819
the past two days.

212
00:18:58,200 --> 00:19:00,180
And they check everyone's ID going in and out now.

213
00:19:00,359 --> 00:19:01,359
It's pretty strict.

214
00:19:05,740 --> 00:19:06,319
Honey,

215
00:19:07,380 --> 00:19:08,140
you must be careful

216
00:19:08,140 --> 00:19:09,140
when you go in and out these two days.

217
00:19:09,839 --> 00:19:10,380
If you have anything,

218
00:19:10,380 --> 00:19:11,380
