223
00:19:21,940 --> 00:19:22,619
You're overreacting again.

224
00:19:23,400 --> 00:19:24,259
Okay.

225
00:19:24,339 --> 00:19:25,519
How can it be so serious?

226
00:19:26,380 --> 00:19:27,339
I'll go to work first.

227
00:19:32,160 --> 00:19:32,940
Be careful.

228
00:19:33,400 --> 00:19:34,700
Don't worry.

229
00:19:52,660 --> 00:19:53,240
Chen Yi,

230
00:19:53,700 --> 00:19:54,700
I'm going to the restroom.

231
00:20:48,579 --> 00:20:49,039
Gone.

232
00:21:01,559 --> 00:21:02,099
There have been a lot of rumors

233
00:21:02,099 --> 00:21:03,599
out there lately.

234
00:21:04,619 --> 00:21:06,279
If brother can't handle it,

235
00:21:09,059 --> 00:21:10,740
don't lose your composure.

236
00:21:11,220 --> 00:21:12,599
You came from under my command.

237
00:21:16,059 --> 00:21:17,119
It's related to the tax bill.

238
00:21:21,559 --> 00:21:22,380
Who told you that?

239
00:21:27,079 --> 00:21:28,880
So many people handle these documents,

240
00:21:29,420 --> 00:21:30,319
so they all

241
00:21:30,640 --> 00:21:32,079
know some information.

242
00:21:37,380 --> 00:21:38,039
Yi,

243
00:21:39,619 --> 00:21:40,940
