244
00:21:42,480 --> 00:21:44,000
I can't hide this from you.

245
00:21:51,440 --> 00:21:52,579
But at this point,

246
00:21:52,579 --> 00:21:54,079
you brought this up to me.

247
00:21:55,079 --> 00:21:55,859
What do you mean?

248
00:22:00,299 --> 00:22:01,500
Are you short of money recently?

249
00:22:06,460 --> 00:22:07,079
Bin,

250
00:22:08,380 --> 00:22:09,599
I'm not so ambitious.

251
00:22:11,839 --> 00:22:13,500
All I want is to open a pool hall with friends,

252
00:22:14,440 --> 00:22:15,920
make a little money on my own

253
00:22:16,880 --> 00:22:17,859
and keep my family secure.

254
00:22:19,519 --> 00:22:20,099
That's enough.

255
00:22:27,920 --> 00:22:28,660
You're my brother.

256
00:22:29,960 --> 00:22:31,500
I'll show you something later.

257
00:22:45,900 --> 00:22:47,420
Monitoring of the security room

258
00:22:48,740 --> 00:22:50,220
is for people outside to see.

259
00:22:54,319 --> 00:22:55,440
This is the real surveillance system.

260
00:22:57,119 --> 00:22:58,200
It covers

261
00:22:58,259 --> 00:22:59,980
all the corners of the whole karaoke hall.

262
00:23:03,240 --> 00:23:04,180
Only you know.

263
00:23:05,619 --> 00:23:06,880
You can't tell outsiders.

264
00:23:11,519 --> 00:23:12,220
Sit down.

265
00:23:23,440 --> 00:23:24,500
Now that you know about

266
00:23:24,500 --> 00:23:25,700
the tax bill.

267
00:23:26,480 --> 00:23:27,099
I won't

268
00:23:27,099 --> 00:23:28,180
hide it anymore.

269
00:23:30,140 --> 00:23:31,400
Me and Zhai Fengmao

270
00:23:32,200 --> 00:23:33,059
are brothers who

271
00:23:33,059 --> 00:23:34,460
have worked hard together,

272
00:23:35,519 --> 00:23:36,960
but people always change.

273
00:23:38,279 --> 00:23:39,779
I've tried to persuade him many times.

274
00:23:40,420 --> 00:23:41,920
After all, he needs to support

275
00:23:42,640 --> 00:23:43,700
all his subordinates.

276
00:23:45,400 --> 00:23:46,779
He used to

277
00:23:47,980 --> 00:23:48,859
listen to me.

278
00:23:49,599 --> 00:23:50,359
Now...

279
00:23:54,460 --> 00:23:55,140
Yi,

280
00:23:56,099 --> 00:23:56,799
do you remember

281
00:23:56,799 --> 00:23:58,200
when we first met?

282
00:24:00,640 --> 00:24:01,160
Yes.

283
00:24:03,500 --> 00:24:04,720
After a ball game,

284
00:24:06,319 --> 00:24:07,880
I was surrounded in the alley and beaten.

285
00:24:09,259 --> 00:24:10,880
You happened to walk by and saved me.

286
00:24:21,619 --> 00:24:22,220
This is

287
00:24:22,220 --> 00:24:23,440
when we first met.

288
00:24:42,480 --> 00:24:43,059
Bin,

289
00:24:43,700 --> 00:24:44,299
I don't want it.

290
00:24:53,200 --> 00:24:54,259
These years,

291
00:24:55,779 --> 00:24:56,680
for me,

292
00:24:57,579 --> 00:24:58,420
